      "description": "## Move to New Folder 1.0.0\n\nInitial public release.\n\n### Features\n- Move files into newly created folders from the file explorer or command palette\n- Move folders into newly created folders from the file explorer\n- Searchable parent-folder picker\n- Inline folder-name validation based on the current platform\n- Existing-folder reuse flow with back navigation\n- Safe move operations through Obsidian APIs\n\n### Release assets\n- main.js\n- manifest.json\n- styles.css\n",
